\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The act of playing through the game and figuring out the mystery is quite the experience, and nothing quite like it has ever been done since. Since most players bought the game used, without a manual, the code was constantly published in Nintendo Power, but for those that solved the puzzle firsthand, it remains a great moment in gaming. The Virtual Console release of the game includes the letter in with the digital manual, and at the bottom of the screen is a small pail of water, which is Nintendo\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s way of trying to be true to the material.}
